latestIgtvVideos.title: Blowout & Style Routine 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is my go to routine for achieving bouncy soft curls that loosen into waves! 

1. Start with sectioned (damp) hair- clip hair on top and start from the bottom.

2. Apply a dime size amount of @loreal Elvive Dream Lengths leave-in conditioner (this is also a great heat protectant!)

3. Blowdry through 💨 and braid into sections.

4. Unravel braids & part a thin section of hair to straighten. 

5. Apply flat iron to root and pull through, flip iron under halfway through the ends to create slight curl. 

6. Alternate curling towards and away from your face to create individual curls. 

7. All Done! Enjoy your slay 😉💁🏽‍♀️
